Package: BAZE
Title: Bayesian Tree-Based Selection of Microbiome Features with Enhanced Visualizations
Version: 1.0
Author: Ruitao Liu [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Ruitao Liu <rxl761@case.edu>
Description: A user-friendly, open-source tool for advanced microbiome data analysis,
    visualization, and interpretation using a Bayesian tree-based method
    based on Liangliang Zhang's approach (2018).
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
